# Puchi Frontend

Puchi là nền tảng web học tiếng Việt. Frontend dùng **Next.js 16 (App Router) + React 19**.

## Tech Stack

| Thành phần | Công nghệ |
|------------|-----------|
| Framework | Next.js 16 (App Router, output: standalone) |
| UI | Tailwind CSS v4 + Shadcn UI (New York) |
| State | Zustand v5 |
| Auth | Zitadel (self-host) — `@zitadel/next-auth` + Auth.js OIDC + Custom Login UI |
| i18n | next-intl (9 ngôn ngữ) |
| Animation | Motion + Rive |
| Runtime | Bun (install) + Node.js 22 (build & run) |

## Auth — Zitadel

**Đã migrate từ SuperTokens → Zitadel.** Auth flow:

### Auth.js config
```typescript
// src/lib/auth.ts
NextAuth({
  providers: [Zitadel({ clientId, issuer: "https://auth.puchi.io.vn" })],
  session: { strategy: "jwt" },
});
```

### Typed API Contracts Pattern
- Define request/response contracts trong `src/lib/api-contracts.ts` (APILogin, APIRegister, APIForgotPassword, APIResetPassword)
- API handler wrapper: `src/lib/api-handler.ts` — `defaultHandler<T>()` auto-parses body, validates với Zod schema, trả về typed response
- Mỗi route dùng `defaultHandler` với typed contract để đảm bảo type safety
- `src/config/env.ts` (Zod-validated env config) validate biến môi trường ở runtime

### Auth flow tổng thể
```
Browser → custom form → Next.js API Route → Zitadel Session API
       → redirect OIDC authorize → Auth.js callback → JWT session cookie
```

## Docker Build

Multi-stage build với Bun + Node.js:

| Stage | Image | Purpose |
|-------|-------|---------|
| deps | `oven/bun:1.2-slim` | Install dependencies |
| builder | `node:22-alpine` | Build Next.js |
| runner | `node:22-alpine` | Run production (non-root user nextjs) |

Build args từ CI/CD:
- `NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL` — https://puchi.io.vn
- `NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL` — https://api.puchi.io.vn

## CI/CD

GitHub Actions (`ci-cd.yml`):
- **Lint**: Bun install → ESLint
- **Build & Push**: Docker login GHCR → Build + Push (tag: latest + sha)
- **Build args**: NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL, NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL, NEXT_PUBLIC_WEBSITE_DOMAIN
- **Registry**: `ghcr.io/puchidemy/puchi-frontend`

## Key Env Vars

| Env | Production value | Notes |
|-----|-----------------|-------|
| `NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL` | `https://puchi.io.vn` | App domain |
| `NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL` | `https://api.puchi.io.vn` | API gateway (Envoy Gateway) |
| `NEXT_PUBLIC_WEBSITE_DOMAIN` | `https://puchi.io.vn` | Website domain |
| `ZITADEL_CLIENT_ID` | `382000685111116512` | OIDC client |
| `ZITADEL_ISSUER` | `https://auth.puchi.io.vn` | Zitadel issuer |
| `ZITADEL_INTERNAL_URL` | `http://zitadel.puchi-auth.svc:8080` | Internal cluster DNS |
| `ZITADEL_SERVICE_TOKEN` | (secret) | Service user PAT |
| `AUTH_SECRET` | (secret) | Auth.js secret |
| `AUTH_URL` | `https://puchi.io.vn` | Auth.js URL |
| `NEXTAUTH_URL` | `https://puchi.io.vn` | Auth.js URL |
| `GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID/SECRET` | (secret) | Google OAuth |
| `FACEBOOK_CLIENT_ID/SECRET` | (secret) | Facebook OAuth |
| `TIKTOK_CLIENT_KEY/SECRET` | (secret) | TikTok OAuth |

## Scripts

```bash
bun install          # Cài dependencies
bun run dev          # Dev server (webpack mode)
bun run build        # Build production (chạy bằng Node.js)
bun run start        # Start production
bun run lint         # ESLint
```

## Cấu trúc thư mục

```
src/
├── app/[locale]/     # Next.js App Router pages (i18n)
├── app/api/auth/     # Auth.js + Custom login API routes + typed contracts
├── components/       # UI components (Shadcn + custom)
├── actions/          # Server Actions (logout, etc.)
├── lib/              # Auth.js config, api-contracts.ts, api-handler.ts, Zitadel service client
├── store/            # Zustand stores
├── hooks/            # Custom hooks
├── i18n/             # Translation config
├── styles/           # Global styles
├── constants/        # Constants
├── config/           # env.ts (Zod-validated env config)
├── middleware/       # proxy.ts (request proxy)
└── types/            # TypeScript types
```

## Kết nối Backend

- API qua Envoy Gateway tại `api.puchi.io.vn`
- Auth: Zitadel (internal, không expose ra ngoài)
